---
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Button from "../../components/Button.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Extension Privacy Policy - {SITE_TITLE}</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-black">
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />

    <div
      class="p-6 bg-black text-white flex justify-center pt-10 animate-fade-in opacity-0 [--animation-delay:200ms]"
    >
      <article class="space-y-6 w-full max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Extension Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="text-base font-semibold">
          In short: Flowtide's extension does not store any personally
          identifiable information (PII) about or from you. Any other data is
          collected by Cloudflare to serve wallpaper images to the extension.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base font-semibold">Scope</p>
        <p class="text-base">
          This privacy policy applies to the Flowtide browser extension.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base font-semibold">Terms</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <p class="text-base font-semibold">Flowtide</p>
            <p class="text-base">– The Flowtide browser extension</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-base font-semibold">We/Us</p>
            <p class="text-base">– The developer of Flowtide</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-base font-semibold">PII</p>
            <p class="text-base">– Personally identifiable information</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="text-base font-semibold">CDN</p>
            <p class="text-base">
              – Content Delivery Network - a distributed network of servers
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Data Usage</h2>

        <p class="text-base font-semibold">Image Hosting</p>
        <p class="text-base">
          Flowtide uses Cloudflare’s CDN to host the wallpaper images.
          Cloudflare may collect certain data, including IP addresses and system
          configurations, for performance and security purposes. This data is
          handled by Cloudflare and is subject to their privacy policy. For more
          details, you can refer to Cloudflare's privacy policy.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base font-semibold">Last updated</p>
        <p class="text-base">December 28, 2024</p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <script src="https://scripts.simpleanalyticscdn.com/latest.js"></script>
    <br />
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
